  <brief_title>Flu-Bu-Mel Based Conditioning Regimen for Patients With Lymphoid Malignancies Undergoing Allo-HSCT</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Clinical Trial of Flu-Bu-Mel-E (Fludarabine, Busulfan, Melphalan and Etoposide) as Conditioning Regimen for Patients With Lymphoid Malignancies Undergoing Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
