  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this phase II clinical trial, we evaluate the efficacy and feasibility of conditioning&#xD;
      regimen of fludarabine 150mg/m2, busulfan 9.6mg/kg, melphalan 100mg/m2 and etoposide 800mg/m2&#xD;
      in patients with lymphoid malignancies.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
